LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
body.setDirectControl();
```

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
body.directControl = true;
```

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
body.setDirectControl(false);
```

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
body.directControl = false;
```

