TITLE: Creating New User with Email and Password
DESCRIPTION: Creates a new user account using email and password credentials. This method registers a new user in the Firebase Authentication system with the provided email and password.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rexrainbow/phaser3-rex-notes/blob/master/docs/docs/firebase-auth.md#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
firebaseApp.auth().createUserWithEmailAndPassword(email, password).catch(function(error) {
    // Handle Errors here.
    var errorCode = error.code;
    var errorMessage = error.message;
});
```

