TITLE: Loading Script Tag Loader Plugin in Phaser 3 Scene Configuration
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to load the Script Tag Loader plugin in the preload stage of a Phaser 3 scene configuration. It demonstrates adding the plugin to the scene and using it to load a script.
