LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
public getCanvasWidth(): number {
  if (this._model == null) {
    return 0.0;
  }
  return (
    this._model.canvasinfo.CanvasWidth / this._model.canvasinfo.PixelsPerUnit
  );
}
```

