TITLE: Rendering Live2d Model with Projection Matrix in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to set up the projection matrix for rendering a Live2d model, including scaling and view matrix multiplication.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rexrainbow/phaser3-rex-notes/blob/master/plugins/gameobjects/live2d/note.md#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const projection: CubismMatrix44 = new CubismMatrix44();
if(width < height) {
    projection.scale(1.0, width / height);
} else {
    projection.scale(height / width, 1.0);
}

if (this._viewMatrix != null) {
  projection.multiplyByMatrix(this._viewMatrix);
}
```

